::KitKat::

She looked at Quickstrike as Bobertron made off with Cheetor.
"Well, now what?"  She gave a sigh. "My hip is leaking fluid everywhere, 
your foot looks like it came out of the inferno, and I'm sure Stringtra 
could use a rest.  Why don't we go back to this base of yours and recharge.  
We can go after that SLAG when we are fully charged.  Then we can kick his 
metal hide back to Cybertron."
She looked over at Stringtra, "How are you doing?"

Quickstrike:


Quickstrike fired a few more rounds from his cobra blaster at the end of his
arm. He stared at the sight of Bobertron as he started to fade. He slumped
his shoulders, a disappointed look developing on his slim face. "Dang, ah
don't think Megatron's gonna like this."
